m/apps/550320/extras/ea2aa6145b84959e9d290b4bb88d3e81.webm?t=1773933412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/550320/extras/ea2aa6145b84959e9d290b4bb88d3e81.mp4?t=1773933412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/550320/extras/95781ba9a784605d3013d10d6086ae60.webp?t=1773933412\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your name out at the top of the Leaderboard in our daily and weekly challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/550320/extras/01993e7b75d7114505df8c2f26e26ed4.avif?t=1773933412\" width=600 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/550320/extras/5ee648c83f24cf3a1b3febd166b0f237.webp?t=1773933412\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your driving skills, or simply your favourite landscapes, with the integrated Photo and Replay mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/550320/extras/f08da6b9a4487334649aa15bfd1ce54d.poster.avif?t=1773933412\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/550320/extras/f08da6b9a4487334649aa15bfd1ce54d.webm?t=1773933412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/550320/extras/f08da6b9a4487334649aa15bfd1ce54d.mp4?t=1773933412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></